To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private MovingAverageConvergenceDivergence _macd;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_macd = MACD(symbol, fastPeriod, slowPeriod, signalPeriod);

// In OnData()
if (_macd.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "fast", _macd.Fast.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "slow", _macd.Slow.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "signal", _macd.Signal.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "histogram", _macd.Histogram.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "movingaverageconvergencedivergence", _macd.Current.Value);
}
